txt.en: The great Dunlending camp of Wulf's Cleft lies to the south of Avardin and the Starkmoor.
Bedwur instructed you to inflict as much damage as possible upon the army at Wulf's Cleft.
Defeat the enemies from Wulf's Cleft
The great dunlending military camp of Wulf's Cleft lies to the south of Avardin and Starkmoor.
